data.title: Symphony Orchestra
data.text:
Symphony Orchestra

The Symphony Orchestra is lead and conducted by Dr. Kyle Szabo.

Symphony Orchestra is a large ensemble performing standard symphonic literature. Students of all majors and community members are eligible to participate. Regular collaborations with FGCU choral ensembles include an annual Joyful and Triumphant concert and major works such as Mozart’s Requiem and Handel’s Messiah.
